snippet.title: ZELDA OCARINA OF TIME in BANJO KAZOOIE Full mod
snippet.description:
#LegendOfZelda #BanjoKazooie #SuperMario64 
THE LEGEND OF BANJO KAZOOIE - THE JIGGIES OF TIME is a Banjo Kazooie mod in the world of Zelda: Ocarina of Time.
9 Worlds, 100 jiggies, 900 Notes, 5 Mumbo transformations and a LOT OF EASTER EGGS!! 

SUPPORT MY CHANNEL!
https://www.patreon.com/Kurko 
https://www.paypal.me/KurkoMods
https://www.instagram.com/Kurko_mods/
https://twitter.com/Markus_Kurko 
https://www.twitch.tv/kurko_mods
https://www.tiktok.com/@kurko_mods

DOWNLOAD PATCH 1.3 (UPDATED December 6th 2020) 
Drop your "Banjo-Kazooie (U) [!]" rom here https://patch.wedarobi.com/bk_jiggies_of_time
FULL SOUNDTRACK:
https://mega.nz/file/Y0MHXKTK#t_mp7VhwhIizRPDXcNVpd4QySVDKL1LPxmzoS73p4D4
Trailer song by Linus Olsson:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCXeLLsQaqpu5q9Ivuoc9Z4g
